| `Source/ConvolutionFunctions/riscv_nn_conv_1x1_HWC_s8_s8_s8_asym_bias_fast_any.c` | T5+T6 (tiled conv), T13 (weight contrib) |
| `internal/internal_vec_isa.h` + `internal_vec_isa_v1_0.h` | Vector intrinsic abstractions, macro definitions |

